      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DYNAMITE DOUG (2) generally flies the lids but last time was always well back and ran below best, finishing sixth (17.75) in a Grade 5 at Healesville. Has ability and looks hard to stop. MIGHTY HERCULES (6) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (26.84) in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning 14 races. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Can figure in the finish. WEIRD KAREN (4) was game in defeat off the inside draw last start, finishing second and beaten 1.3 lengths (24.95) behind Our Mabel at Sale. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Must be included in calculations. WILE COYOTE (8) can sneak into the finish again.",
